      "patch": "@@ -0,0 +1,6 @@\n+created: 2026-01-04\n+title: Initial Release Version Bumping\n+intro: >-\n+  This release adds initial release support with implicit version bumping and\n+\n+  fixes row numbering in multi-project views."
    },
    {
      "sha": "1995c5fac0587987baa8c1a66e135f4f579e2141",
      "filename": "changelog/releases/v0.19.1/notes.md",
      "status": "added",
      "additions": 23,
      "deletions": 0,
      "changes": 23,
      "blob_url": "https://github.com/tenzir/ship/blob/6d7753f1ad0c49a5e0bb6a958ad92d328b20940b/changelog%2Freleases%2Fv0.19.1%2Fnotes.md",
      "raw_url": "https://github.com/tenzir/ship/raw/6d7753f1ad0c49a5e0bb6a958ad92d328b20940b/changelog%2Freleases%2Fv0.19.1%2Fnotes.md",
      "contents_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/tenzir/ship/contents/changelog%2Freleases%2Fv0.19.1%2Fnotes.md?ref=6d7753f1ad0c49a5e0bb6a958ad92d328b20940b",
      "patch": "@@ -0,0 +1,23 @@\n+This release adds initial release support with implicit version bumping and fixes row numbering in multi-project views.\n+\n+## \ud83d\ude80 Features\n+\n+### Implicit base version for initial releases\n+\n+When creating the first release, you can now use `--major`, `--minor`, or `--patch` flags without an existing release. The tool uses an implicit `0.0.0` as the base version:\n+\n+- `--major` creates `1.0.0`\n+- `--minor` creates `0.1.0`\n+- `--patch` creates `0.0.1`\n+\n+Previously, these flags required at least one prior release, forcing users to always specify an explicit version for their first release.\n+\n+*By @mavam and @claude.*\n+\n+## \ud83d\udc1e Bug fixes\n+\n+### Correct row numbering in multi-project view\n+\n+Row numbers in multi-project table view now count down from the newest entry, matching single-project behavior. The `show -c <row>` command also resolves row numbers correctly against the displayed table.\n+\n+*By @mavam and @claude.*"
    },
